Volkswagen Seeks Specialist Engineers, Handelsblatt Reports

-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 
2011-07-28T04:58:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/volkswagen-seeks-specialist-engineers-handelsblatt-reports.html
Volkswagen AG wants to hire
specialist engineers and is looking outside  Germany  and
especially in  Spain ,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing Chief
Executive Officer  Martin Winterkorn .  The company is especially looking for engineers in the
areas of electro-mobility, lightweight and vehicle electronics,
according to Winterkorn, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story: Ragnhild Kjetland in
Frankfurt at   rkjetland@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  